response.original_title: Pat Cahill - Uncle Len Needs A New Part For His Hoover
response.overview: Old new act, Pat Cahill, brings another hour of his confused neo-music hall stupidity to the Fringe. Expect earworms, knee ants and eye mice as he gently impresses you in the afternoon with a bit of singing, a bit of stand-up and a bit of dancing. It will all mean something, but you'll have to work that out.
